commit.message:
Wip Qt6 port (#278)

* Initial port to Qt6

* Update .gitignore from lxqt-panel repository

* Replace QScopedPointer with std::unique_ptr

* Port to QRegularExpression

- Clazy suggests static QRegularExpression

* Replace QPair with std::pair

- In Qt6 QPair is an alias for std::pair
- Replace qMakePair() with std::make_pair
- Fix compilation for wrong template argument conversion

* Replace qAsConst() with std::as_const()

* Config DefaultModel: unneeded temporary container

Detected by Clazy

* Qt::AA_UseHighDpiPixmaps is deprecated

High-DPI Pixmaps are always enabled in Qt6

* Fix symbol exporting

Macro names must be different between base library and UI library.
Names are also visible to any project linking to this libraries
so they must be unique,
otherwise we get name clashes like this one.
